name: Ultimate Arcade Games
overview: Ultimate Arcade Games is a collection of 12 arcade-style games, inspired by a variety of popular classics. Each game utilizes core gameplay ideas from classic arcade games, while expanding and improving each game for a new generation of gamers. The games include: • Asteroid Mine • BeeKeeper • ChipBot • FlipSide • Galaxy Hero • Gridlock • Highway 51 • Merchant Galactic • Milk Run • Omega Force • Rubes Cubes • Treasure Hunter
